narration_text: #C C pours the salt into the food
#C C puts the spoon back into the can
#C C pours the minced meat into the mix
#C C throws the paper bag down
#C C picks up the salt can
#C C pours the salt into the water
#C C puts the spoon back into the can
#C C picks up the water container
#C C pours some water into the food
#C C puts the water container down
